# Force LF line endings for text files, regardless of platform or local
# git config (core.autocrlf). This prevents CRLF from being reintroduced
# by Windows editors/tools and silently breaking exact-string JSON
# comparisons in tests (see: GoalSerializerTest CRLF mismatch, Issue #38).

* text=auto eol=lf

*.java text eol=lf
*.json text eol=lf
*.gradle text eol=lf
*.md text eol=lf
*.yml text eol=lf
*.yaml text eol=lf
*.properties text eol=lf

# Windows-specific scripts should keep CRLF
*.bat text eol=crlf

# Binary files — do not touch
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.jar binary
